### 环境配置说明
# 上面已设置默认的local环境变量，可直接运行
# 如需切换环境，请在IntelliJ IDEA中选择对应环境: local/gateway
# 或者手动修改上面的@变量值


### 请求 /create 接口 => 创建函数
POST {{baseUrl}}/formula/excute/engine/executeFormula
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

##
{
    "formula": "LEFT(paramA, length)",
    "parameters": {
        "paramA": "HELLO",
        "length": 5
    }
}

### 请求 /create 接口 => 创建函数
POST {{baseUrl}}/formula/excute/engine/executeFormula
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "formula": "CEILING(订单编号，AVERAGEA(发货地址，联系电话))",
    "parameters": {"订单编号":"001","发货地址":"003","联系电话":"005"}
}

### 请求 /execute 接口 => 执行函数函数 获取人员信息
POST {{baseUrl}}/formula/excute/engine/execute-formula1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "formula": "GETUSER(id,name,'id')",
  "parameters": {}
}

### 请求 /execute 接口 => 执行函数函数 获取人员信息
POST {{baseUrl}}/formula/excute/engine/execute-formula1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "formula": "LEFT(text,length)",
  "parameters": {"text": "name", "length": 2}
}

### 请求 /create 接口 => 创建函数
POST {{baseUrl}}/formula/excute/engine/executeFormula
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "formula": "SUMIF(#X.A, >10, #X.B)"
}

### 执行公式计算
POST {{baseUrl}}/formula/excute/engine/execute-formula1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "formula": "=SUM(A1:A10)",
  "parameters": {
    "A1": 10,
    "A2": 20,
    "A3": 30
  }
}

### 验证公式语法
POST {{baseUrl}}/formula/excute/engine/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "formula": "=SUM(A1:A10)"
}